ActBroadcasting Act
PrecisAppointment of GUY FOURNIER of Abbotsford, Quebec, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Broadcasting Corporation to hold office during good behaviour for a term of four years, in the place of Roy Heenan, whose term has expired.
